SQL.create: CREATE TABLE Person(id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(30), gender VARCHAR(10), phoneNumber VARCHAR(10), signUpDate DATE)
CREATE TABLE Seeker(pid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, FOREIGN KEY(pid) REFERENCES Person(id) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE CASCADE)
CREATE TABLE Landlord(pid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, FOREIGN KEY(pid) REFERENCES Person(id) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE CASCADE)
CREATE TABLE Location(city VARCHAR(50) PRIMARY KEY, transportation VARCHAR(255), stores VARCHAR(255), entertainment CHAR(255), crimeRate REAL)

SQL.create: CREATE TABLE Housing(streetAddress CHAR(30), postalCode CHAR(7), city CHAR(30) NOT NULL, postTitle CHAR(30), price REAL, squareFootage INTEGER, roomsAvailable INTEGER, accommodations CHAR(140), createdOn DATE, updatedOn DATE, landlordPID INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(streetAddress, postalCode), FOREIGN KEY(city) REFERENCES Location(city) ON DELETE NO ACTION, FOREIGN KEY(landlordPID) REFERENCES Landlord(pid) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE CASCADE)

data.accommodations: Couches, beds, dish washer and oven

SQL.create: CREATE TABLE History(hid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, moveInDate DATE, moveOutDate DATE, streetAddress CHAR(30) NOT NULL, postalCode CHAR(7) NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY(streetAddress, postalCode) REFERENCES Housing(streetAddress, postalCode) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE Occupies(pid INTEGER, current INTEGER, previous INTEGER, PRIMARY KEY(pid, current), FOREIGN KEY(pid) REFERENCES Seeker(pid) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, FOREIGN KEY(current) REFERENCES History(hid) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, FOREIGN KEY(previous) REFERENCES History(hid) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE)
